Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的村子已經在400年間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斷和外界的接觸  過著自給自足的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂夏至祭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是迎接在夏天回來的先祖們的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱豐收的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從明天的黎明開始  夜晚結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們可以待到那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啊  那玫瑰窗和尖塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像以前繪畫裡的中世紀教堂一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這邊的也很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個水井真是老古董啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶的山裡住著野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這村裡住著的人不就是狼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼  我們是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使和下面的人種族不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和柯蒂麗亞長得一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那時我還是個孩子  但我記得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷曼妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她給這間宅子  這個村子帶來了無法消除的災禍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷曼妮！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.69,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(653,545)}在夏至祭降下神諭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件發生在狄奧多村長的書房
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜裡十二點在書房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女僕…對了  當時還是十五歲的柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有去更換水壺裡的水的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天也正好是在十二點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道是正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和其他人看到了打開鎖進去的柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我用懷錶確認了一下時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知為何  和我一起的人對時間的證詞都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入書房的柯蒂麗亞馬上就發出了尖叫  跑了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匆忙趕過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奧多村長已經被短刀刺中身亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板上不知為何散落著很多金幣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金幣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為這個村子不使用金幣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時都由狄奧多村長統一保管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天晚上開始  柯蒂麗亞就發高燒臥床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到她退燒  成為下一任村長的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將她放逐出了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐出？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她拿著一枚金幣和一個旅行箱離開村子之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就升起了那座吊橋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未離開過村子不諳世事的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都懷疑她能不能平安活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人不能放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則會給村裡帶來災禍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那個柯蒂麗亞的女兒卻在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散什麼步啊  明明剛剛才到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是謝爾吉斯村長的助手  安普羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  為什麼皮膚和頭髮的顏色不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道外面世界的人不都只是金髮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加  幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個地方想讓你給我帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說  不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換  可以讓我再摸這個人一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂麗亞住過的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟帶我們來這種地方被人知道了可不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是什麼都沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:06:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯蒂麗亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和還是嬰兒的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是柯蒂麗亞十五歲時就被趕出這裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走了留在這裡的什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後留下了長大後柯蒂麗亞的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這混沌究竟指向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奧多…前任村長的墓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對墳墓做這種遭天譴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我不是罪人  C」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂麗亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是柯蒂麗亞寫下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親果然是因為冤罪被趕出村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  真正的罪人會在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…和維多利加一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  電話怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜德蕊小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有電話也就是說  果然這裡通著電吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  村長不是說過的是自給自足的生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問了那個奇怪的女僕才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是有贊助人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊助人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  名字叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個叫布萊恩·羅斯可的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩…羅斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是離開村子在外面生活的人的子孫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約在十年前他出了一筆錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牌也打膩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  去教堂看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛剛有狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西  那個可怕的老頭會把它們趕跑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又纏到一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繫帶和荷葉邊太多叫人頭暈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前來的布萊恩·羅斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是為了什麼目的來到這個村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了給村裡拉電線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到十年前  就是上次世界大戰發生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這個時代給深山裡拉電線太匆忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  十年前的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也符合那張照片拍攝的年代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是洗澡的熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請摻入涼水使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有澡可以洗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加  發生什麼事的話要叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡守著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  哦  哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}我喜歡洗澡～啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx70\fscy70}因為暖洋洋～啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  是唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於像是變回平時的維多利加了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有回應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了久城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想嚇唬我  把我從村裡趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧  這個村子有種不祥的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會保護我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  這是紅蕪菁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台花車是冬之軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在這個廣場上村裡的男人們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會分為夏之軍和冬之軍演一場打仗的戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之軍要把冬之軍的主將冬之男打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和花車一起點火燒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要侮辱這個村子的話就滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊  相信迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個晦氣的村子  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  要是現在被趕出這村子的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  到哪都是一副壞脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回房間去吧  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙昨晚也在教堂幹了壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在村裡人的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把裝飾的古壺往裝聖水的水缸裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗通一下丟了進去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發酒瘋的話我可聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還笑著說「是這種破爛貨  為什麼還當寶」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖彼得也會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  祭典的點心  我拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亞朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說了那些話  果然還是在意祭典的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個有什麼意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是安普羅茲先生吧  好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之男啊  燃燒消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是假人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿水來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亞朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞  亞朗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算妨礙祭典來找碴而和假人交換了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾吉斯村長  那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在少女們扔榛果的時候  這個年輕人走過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:16:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣場也聚集了很多人  是不可能和假人交換的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴是愚者的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏至祭是不能中止的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來教堂還有儀式  我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都有人死了  居然還要繼續祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪啊  這個村子裡的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  維多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會保護我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌先生  你也是詢問未來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之軍勝利了  約定豐收之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚時分就要將教堂清空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教堂是通往陰間的出入口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為來看豐收的祖先們的通路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  接近這裡的祖先們的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會通過村長回答孩子們的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌先生  機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和維多利加…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等下  安普羅茲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我是來找維多利加的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個女孩和你是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你想問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  我有一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道和維多利加以後也能一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幾年之後  會吹起撼動世界的狂風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的身體太輕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那陣狂風  你們兩人將會分開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  心將永遠不會分離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會分開…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問了能不能長高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長高是指什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是受盡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不說一聲說就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才都跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書房
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奧多村長就這樣被刺中後背  那把短刀直沒到刀柄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奧多大人是成年人  柯蒂麗亞是十五歲的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高差很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  對孩子夠不到的後背
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能將短刀插沒到刀柄的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人柯蒂麗亞  那污穢的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果  或者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人另有其人  你是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧之泉在對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在碎片全部重新拼湊完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新拼湊完成  那知道誰是犯人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算知道誰是犯人  證明它的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有人死了  就算狼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏至祭也不允許中止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經聽不到狼的聲音了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了  安普羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第二個了  久城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的罪惡閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.17,0:24:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的罪惡將其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.87,0:24:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會  有非常不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:21.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(641,556)}過去的王國裡迴盪著長嘯


